        <h4>Jazz Guitar Solo</h4>
        <a href="#rose-room">Rose Room - Charlie Christian</a>
        <a href="#so-what">So What - Miles Davis</a>
        <a href="#after-hours">After Hours - Ronny Jordan</a>
        <a href="#blues-in-c">Blues In C - Barney Kessel</a>
        <h4>Jazz Guitar Melodic Style</h4>
        <a href="#smile">Smile - Charlie Chaplin</a>
        <a href="#moonlight-in-vermont">Moonlight In Vermont - Alex Farran</a>
        <h4>Akkordfolge Übungen</h4>
        <a href="#chord-progression-exercise">Akkordfolge Übungen</a>
      </aside>
      <a href="#top" class="scroll-top" aria-label="Zurück nach oben">⬆</a>
